<h2 id="first-version---not-thread-safe">First version - not thread-safe</h2>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-c#" data-lang="c#"><span style="color:#228b22">// Bad code! Do not use!
</span><span style="color:#228b22"></span><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">public</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">sealed</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">class</span> <span style="color:#008b45;font-weight:bold">Singleton</span>
{
  <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">private</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">static</span> Singleton instance = <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">null</span>;

  <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">private</span> Singleton()
  {
  }

  <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">public</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">static</span> Singleton Instance
  {
    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">get</span>
    {
      <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span> (instance == <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">null</span>)
      {
        instance = <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">new</span> Singleton();
      }
      <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> instance;
    }
  }
}
</code></pre></div><p>å¦‚å‰æ‰€è¿°ï¼Œä»¥ä¸Šå†…å®¹ä¸æ˜¯çº¿ç¨‹å®‰å…¨çš„ã€‚</p>
<p>ä¸¤ä¸ªä¸åŒçš„çº¿ç¨‹éƒ½å¯ä»¥æ‰§è¡Œåˆ¤æ–­ï¼ˆ<em>evaluated the test</em>ï¼‰<code>if(instance == null)</code>å¹¶å‘ç°å®ƒä¸º<code>true</code>ï¼Œç„¶åéƒ½åˆ›å»ºå®ä¾‹ï¼Œè¿™è¿åäº†å•ä¾‹æ¨¡å¼ã€‚è¯·æ³¨æ„ï¼Œå®é™…ä¸Šå¯èƒ½å·²ç»åœ¨è®¡ç®—è¡¨è¾¾å¼ä¹‹å‰åˆ›å»ºäº†å®ä¾‹ï¼Œä½†æ˜¯å†…å­˜æ¨¡å‹ä¸èƒ½ä¿è¯å®ä¾‹çš„æ–°å€¼èƒ½æš´éœ²ç»™å…¶ä»–çº¿ç¨‹ï¼Œé™¤éå·²ä¼ é€’é€‚å½“çš„å†…å­˜å±éšœï¼ˆäº’æ–¥é”ï¼‰ï¼ˆ<em>memory barriers</em>ï¼‰ã€‚</p>
<h2 id="second-version---simple-thread-safety">Second version - simple thread-safety</h2>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-C#" data-lang="C#"><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">public</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">sealed</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">class</span> <span style="color:#008b45;font-weight:bold">Singleton</span>
{
  <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">private</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">static</span> Singleton instance = <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">null</span>;
  <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">private</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">static</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">readonly</span> <span style="color:#00688b;font-weight:bold">object</span> padlock = <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">new</span> <span style="color:#00688b;font-weight:bold">object</span>();

  Singleton()
  {
  }

  <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">public</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">static</span> Singleton Instance
  {
    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">get</span>
    {
      <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">lock</span> (padlock)
      {
        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span> (instance == <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">null</span>)
        {
          instance = <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">new</span> Singleton();
        }
        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> instance;
      }
    }
  }
}
</code></pre></div><p>æ­¤å®ç°æ˜¯çº¿ç¨‹å®‰å…¨çš„ã€‚çº¿ç¨‹åœ¨å…±äº«å¯¹è±¡ä¸ŠåŠ é”ï¼ˆ<em>takes out a lock</em>ï¼‰ï¼Œç„¶ååœ¨åˆ›å»ºå®ä¾‹ä¹‹å‰æ£€æŸ¥æ˜¯å¦å·²åˆ›å»ºå®ä¾‹ã€‚è¿™å¯ä»¥è§£å†³å†…å­˜å±éšœé—®é¢˜ï¼ˆå› ä¸ºé”å®šå¯ç¡®ä¿æ‰€æœ‰è¯»å–å‡åœ¨è·å–é”ä¹‹åé€»è¾‘å‘ç”Ÿï¼Œè€Œè§£é”å¯ç¡®ä¿æ‰€æœ‰å†™å…¥å‡åœ¨é”é‡Šæ”¾ä¹‹å‰é€»è¾‘å‘ç”Ÿï¼‰å¹¶ç¡®ä¿åªæœ‰ä¸€ä¸ªçº¿ç¨‹å°†åˆ›å»ºä¸€ä¸ªå®ä¾‹ï¼ˆä»…ä¸€ä¸ªçº¿ç¨‹ä¸€æ¬¡å¯ä»¥ä½äºä»£ç çš„è¯¥éƒ¨åˆ†ä¸­ï¼Œåˆ°ç¬¬äºŒä¸ªçº¿ç¨‹è¿›å…¥è¯¥çº¿ç¨‹æ—¶ï¼Œç¬¬ä¸€ä¸ªçº¿ç¨‹å°†åˆ›å»ºè¯¥å®ä¾‹ï¼Œå› æ­¤è¯¥è¡¨è¾¾å¼çš„è®¡ç®—ç»“æœä¸º<code>false</code>ï¼‰ã€‚ä¸å¹¸çš„æ˜¯ï¼Œæ¯æ¬¡è¯·æ±‚å®ä¾‹æ—¶éƒ½éœ€è¦è·å–é”ï¼Œå› æ­¤æ€§èƒ½ä¼šå—åˆ°å½±å“ã€‚</p>
<p>è¯·æ³¨æ„ï¼Œæˆ‘æ²¡æœ‰åƒæ­¤å®ç°çš„æŸäº›ç‰ˆæœ¬é‚£æ ·é”å®š<code>typeof(Singleton)</code>ï¼Œè€Œæ˜¯é”å®šäº†ç±»ç§æœ‰çš„é™æ€å˜é‡çš„å€¼ã€‚é”å®šå…¶ä»–ç±»å¯ä»¥è®¿é—®å’Œé”å®šçš„å¯¹è±¡ï¼ˆsuch as the typeï¼‰å¯èƒ½ä¼šå¯¼è‡´æ€§èƒ½é—®é¢˜ç”šè‡³æ­»é”ã€‚è¿™æ˜¯æˆ‘çš„ä¸€èˆ¬æ ·å¼é¦–é€‰é¡¹-å°½å¯èƒ½ä»…é”å®šä¸“é—¨ä¸ºé”å®šç›®çš„è€Œåˆ›å»ºçš„å¯¹è±¡ï¼Œæˆ–è€…ä¸ºç‰¹å®šç›®çš„è€Œå°†å…¶é”å®šåœ¨å“ªä¸ªæ–‡æ¡£ä¸Šï¼ˆä¾‹å¦‚ç”¨äºç­‰å¾…/è§¦å‘é˜Ÿåˆ—ï¼‰ã€‚é€šå¸¸ï¼Œæ­¤ç±»å¯¹è±¡åº”ä¸ºä½¿ç”¨å®ƒä»¬çš„ç±»æ‰€ä¸“ç”¨ã€‚è¿™æœ‰åŠ©äºä½¿ç¼–å†™çº¿ç¨‹å®‰å…¨çš„åº”ç”¨ç¨‹åºå˜å¾—æ›´åŠ å®¹æ˜“ã€‚</p>
<h2 id="third-version---attempted-thread-safety-using-double-check-locking">Third version - attempted thread-safety using double-check locking</h2>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-c#" data-lang="c#"><span style="color:#228b22">// Bad code! Do not use!
</span><span style="color:#228b22"></span><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">public</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">sealed</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">class</span> <span style="color:#008b45;font-weight:bold">Singleton</span>
{
  <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">private</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">static</span> Singleton instance = <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">null</span>;
  <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">private</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">static</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">readonly</span> <span style="color:#00688b;font-weight:bold">object</span> padlock = <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">new</span> <span style="color:#00688b;font-weight:bold">object</span>();

  Singleton()
  {
  }

  <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">public</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">static</span> Singleton Instance
  {
    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">get</span>
    {
      <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span> (instance == <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">null</span>)
      {
        <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">lock</span> (padlock)
        {
          <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">if</span> (instance == <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">null</span>)
          {
            instance = <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">new</span> Singleton();
          }
        }
      }
      <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> instance;
    }
  }
}
</code></pre></div><p>æ­¤å®ç°æ–¹å¼ï¼ˆ<em>implementation</em>ï¼‰å°è¯•ä¸å†æ¯æ¬¡éƒ½åŠ é”ï¼ŒåŒæ—¶ä¿è¯çº¿ç¨‹å®‰å…¨ã€‚é—æ†¾çš„æ˜¯ï¼Œè¯¥æ¨¡å¼æœ‰å››ä¸ªç¼ºç‚¹ï¼ˆ<em>there are four downsides to the pattern</em>ï¼‰ï¼š</p>
<ul>
<li>å®ƒåœ¨Javaä¸­ä¸èµ·ä½œç”¨ã€‚è¿™ä¹ˆè¯´è¿™ä¼¼ä¹æœ‰äº›ä¸åˆç†ï¼Œä½†æ˜¯å€¼å¾—ä¸€æçš„æ˜¯ï¼Œæ‚¨æ˜¯å¦éœ€è¦Javaä¸­çš„å•ä¾‹æ¨¡å¼ï¼ŒCï¼ƒç¨‹åºå‘˜ä¹Ÿå¾ˆå¯èƒ½æ˜¯Javaç¨‹åºå‘˜ã€‚ Javaå†…å­˜æ¨¡å‹æ— æ³•ç¡®ä¿åœ¨å°†å¯¹æ–°å¯¹è±¡çš„å¼•ç”¨åˆ†é…ç»™å®ä¾‹ä¹‹å‰ï¼Œæ‰§è¡Œå®Œæ„é€ å‡½æ•°ã€‚ Javaå†…å­˜æ¨¡å‹é’ˆå¯¹1.5ç‰ˆè¿›è¡Œäº†é‡æ–°åŠ å·¥ï¼Œä½†æ˜¯åœ¨æ­¤ä¹‹åï¼Œåœ¨æ²¡æœ‰æ˜“å¤±æ€§å˜é‡çš„æƒ…å†µä¸‹ï¼ŒåŒé‡æ£€æŸ¥é”å®šä»ç„¶è¢«ç ´åï¼ˆåƒCï¼ƒä¸€æ ·ï¼‰ã€‚</li>
<li>æ²¡æœ‰ä»»ä½•å†…å­˜éšœç¢ï¼Œå®ƒåœ¨<code>ECMA CLI</code>è§„èŒƒä¸­ä¹Ÿè¢«æ‰“ç ´ã€‚åœ¨.NET 2.0å†…å­˜æ¨¡å‹ï¼ˆæ¯”ECMAè§„èŒƒæ›´å¼ºï¼‰ä¸‹ï¼Œå®ƒå¾ˆå¯èƒ½æ˜¯å®‰å…¨çš„ï¼Œä½†æˆ‘å®æ„¿ä¸ä¾èµ–é‚£äº›æ›´å¼ºçš„è¯­ä¹‰ï¼Œå°¤å…¶æ˜¯åœ¨å¯¹å®‰å…¨æ€§æœ‰ä»»ä½•ç–‘é—®çš„æƒ…å†µä¸‹ã€‚å°†å®ä¾‹å˜é‡è®¾ç½®ä¸º<code>volatile</code>ä¹Ÿæœ‰æ•ˆï¼Œå°±åƒæ˜¾å¼çš„å†…å­˜å±éšœè°ƒç”¨ä¸€æ ·ï¼Œä½†è¿™æ ·çš„è¯å³ä½¿æ˜¯å¤§ä½¬ä¹Ÿæ— æ³•ç¡®åˆ‡åœ°ç¡®å®šéœ€è¦å“ªäº›å±éšœã€‚æˆ‘å€¾å‘äºä¸å»ç”¨å¤§ä½¬ä»¬æœ‰äº‰è®®çš„æ–¹æ³•ï¼</li>
<li>å¾ˆå®¹æ˜“å‡ºé”™ã€‚è¯¥æ¨¡å¼å¿…é¡»ä¸ä¸Šé¢çš„å®Œå…¨ä¸€æ ·-ä»»ä½•é‡å¤§æ›´æ”¹éƒ½å¯èƒ½å½±å“æ€§èƒ½æˆ–æ­£ç¡®æ€§ã€‚</li>
<li>å®ƒçš„æ€§èƒ½ä»ç„¶ä¸å¦‚åæ¥çš„å®ç°æ–¹å¼ã€‚</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="fourth-version---not-quite-as-lazy-but-thread-safe-without-using-locks">Fourth version - not quite as lazy, but thread-safe without using locks</h2>
<div class="highlight"><pre style="background-color:#eed;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4"><code class="language-c#" data-lang="c#"><span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">public</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">sealed</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">class</span> <span style="color:#008b45;font-weight:bold">Singleton</span>
{
  <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">private</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">static</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">readonly</span> Singleton instance = <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">new</span> Singleton();

  <span style="color:#228b22">// Explicit static constructor to tell C# compiler
</span><span style="color:#228b22"></span>  <span style="color:#228b22">// not to mark type as beforefieldinit
</span><span style="color:#228b22"></span>  <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">static</span> Singleton()
  {
  }

  <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">private</span> Singleton()
  {
  }

  <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">public</span> <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">static</span> Singleton Instance
  {
    <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">get</span>
    {
      <span style="color:#8b008b;font-weight:bold">return</span> instance;
    }
  }
}
</code></pre></div><p>å¦‚æ‚¨æ‰€è§ï¼Œè¿™ç¡®å®éå¸¸ç®€å•ï¼Œé‚£å®ƒæ˜¯æ€ä¹ˆå®ç°çº¿ç¨‹å®‰å…¨çš„ï¼Œå®ƒæœ‰å¤šæ‡’å‘¢ï¼ŸWellï¼Œå°†Cï¼ƒä¸­çš„é™æ€æ„é€ å‡½æ•°æŒ‡å®šä¸ºä»…åœ¨åˆ›å»ºç±»çš„å®ä¾‹æˆ–å¼•ç”¨é™æ€æˆå‘˜æ—¶æ‰§è¡Œï¼Œå¹¶ä¸”æ¯ä¸ª<code>AppDomain</code>ä»…æ‰§è¡Œä¸€æ¬¡ã€‚é‰´äºæ— è®ºå…¶ä»–æƒ…å†µå¦‚ä½•éƒ½éœ€è¦æ‰§è¡Œå¯¹æ–°æ„é€ çš„ç±»å‹çš„æ£€æŸ¥ï¼Œå› æ­¤æ¯”åœ¨å‰é¢çš„ç¤ºä¾‹ä¸­æ·»åŠ é¢å¤–çš„æ£€æŸ¥è¦å¿«ã€‚</p>
<p>ä½†æ˜¯ï¼Œè¿™ç§æ–¹æ³•ä¹Ÿæœ‰ä¸€äº›ç¼ºç‚¹ï¼ˆ<em>wrinkles</em>ï¼‰ï¼š</p>
